   "source": [
    "# Selection Sort\n",
    "\n",
    "Selection sort works by selecting the largest value from the range A[0, n) and swapping its location with the rightmost element A[n-1]. This process is repeated, subsequently, on each successive smaller range  A[0, n-1) until A is sorted. "
   ]
